webinarImpressionToImpact.title: From Impressions to Impact: Attribution for DOOH Advertising
webinarImpressionToImpact.description: Join us for a live webinar hosted by Ryan Pogy, Broadsign's Data Partnerships Director, to explore the most effective strategies for DOOH attribution.

webinarMemorableAdvertising.title: Memorable Advertising: Using Brand Lift Studies to Measure DOOH Impact
webinarMemorableAdvertising.description: In this webinar, we'll explain why brand lift studies are a powerful way to measure campaign impact, compare them to other attribution solutions, and provide actionable recommendations on how to run them effectively in your omnichannel strategy.
